---
// DIB welcome screen (FR-002): explains anonymity and routes the employee into
// the form. Dark / DM Sans / emerald aesthetic — design §4.1.
---

<div
  class="font-dm-sans flex min-h-screen flex-col items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f1923] via-[#1a2a3a] to-[#0d2137] px-8 py-16 text-slate-200"
>
  <div class="animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 mx-auto w-full max-w-[640px] text-center duration-500">
    <!-- Eyebrow with pulsing "live" dot (design §4.1) -->
    <div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <div class="h-2.5 w-2.5 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-emerald-600 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(5,150,105,0.5)]"></div>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium tracking-wider text-slate-500 uppercase">Anonimowo · Bezpiecznie · Poufnie</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="mb-4 text-[2rem] leading-tight font-semibold text-slate-100">Podziel się sugestią — anonimowo</h1>

    <p class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-[520px] text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
      Masz pomysł, dostrzegasz problem albo wiesz, co usprawnić? Powiedz nam o tym. Nie zapisujemy Twojego nazwiska,
      adresu e-mail ani adresu IP — wypełnij krótki formularz, a Twoja sugestia trafi prosto do zespołu.
    </p>

    <a
      href="/submit"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-emerald-500 px-8 py-3 text-[0.95rem] font-semibold text-white shadow-[0_4px_24px_rgba(5,150,105,0.3)] transition-all hover:from-emerald-500 hover:to-emerald-400"
    >
      Dalej
      <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>

    <!-- Trust-footer (design §4.1) -->
    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 border-t border-white/[0.05] pt-6">
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-slate-600">🔒 Szyfrowane połączenie</span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-slate-600">👤 Bez logowania</span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-slate-600">🚫 Bez śledzenia</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
